  "Description": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span>LOG CORRUPT <span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span> RECOVERING DAMAGED SECTORS<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br><VAL_ON>\"going from bad to worse<br>can't wait to get home<br>navigation ::: distorted ::: nothing but static<br>warping but ::: just empty systems<br>::: lost in some abandoned sector?\"<>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span>日志损坏<span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span>正在恢复损坏扇区<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br>“<VAL_ON>情况越来越糟了<br>我已经等不及要回家了<br>导航:::失真:::只有静电噪音<br>在曲速航行但:::都只是空荡荡的星系<br>:::在某个被遗弃的星区迷失了吗？”<>",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span> 日誌毀損 <span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span> 正在復原受損區塊 <span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br>「<VAL_ON>情況每況愈下<br>等不及要回家了<br>導航:::扭曲:::只剩雜音<br>進行了空間跳躍但:::空蕩蕩的系統<br>::: 迷失在某個被遺棄的區域？」<>"
  },
